---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Our Story | Sosun Fihaara"
  description="Four decades, four directors, one unwavering commitment to the people of the Maldives. The story of Sosun Fihaara, from a single store on Majeedhee Magu to a nationwide FMCG distribution network."
>
<main>

  <!-- ═══ HERO ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="story-hero">
    <div class="story-hero__inner">
      <p class="story-eyebrow">Est. 1980 &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Mal&eacute;, Maldives</p>
      <h1 class="story-title">SOSUN<br>FIHAARA</h1>
      <p class="story-sub">Decades of Growing Maldives</p>
      <div class="story-divider"></div>
      <p class="story-desc">From a single store on Majeedhee Magu to a network woven into the fabric of Maldivian daily life &mdash; this is our story.</p>
      <p class="story-dates">Since <strong>1980</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div class="scroll-cue">
      <div class="mouse"></div>
      <span>Scroll</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ OPENING ════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="section bg-cream">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:720px; text-align:center;">
      <span class="eyebrow">Our Journey</span>
      <p class="story-quote" style="margin-top:22px;">&ldquo;Four decades. Four directors.<br>One unwavering commitment to the people of Maldives.&rdquo;</p>
      <div class="gold-bar"></div>
      <p style="color:var(--muted); font-size:17px; line-height:1.9;">What began as a humble store has grown into a trusted household name &mdash; a company woven into the fabric of everyday Maldivian life. Behind every milestone stood a team that believed in building something lasting.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ TIMELINE ═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="story-timeline bg-white" id="timeline">
    <div class="story-spine-track">
      <div class="story-spine-fill" id="spineFill"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-head center" style="padding:80px 24px 48px; margin-bottom:0;">
      <span class="eyebrow">A Legacy in Time</span>
      <h2 style="margin-top:14px;">The Milestones That Made Us</h2>
    </div>

    <!-- 1980 -->
    <article class="milestone" data-era="e1980">
      <div class="ms-text">
        <p class="ms-chapter">Our Beginning</p>
        <h2 class="ms-title">A store on<br>Majeedhee Magu</h2>
        <p class="ms-body">In 1980, our founders acquired a modest store on Mal&eacute;'s most vibrant commercial street. It was more than a shop &mdash; it was the seed of a dream, planted in the heart of the Maldives. From those first shelves, a legacy began to take shape.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ms-center">
        <div class="ms-dot"></div>
        <span class="ms-year">1980</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ms-img-wrap">
        <div class="era e1980">
          <div class="era-bg" data-parallax></div>
          <div class="era-watermark">1980</div>
          <svg class="era-arch" viewBox="0 0 600 140" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
