        <h2 class="ms-title">Expo Investments &amp;<br>First Imports</h2>
        <p class="ms-body">Fifteen years into our journey, we formalized our vision with the establishment of Expo Investments. Our first foray into imports &mdash; Promina baby food &mdash; marked our belief that Maldivians deserved access to quality from around the world. SOSUN was growing beyond a single store.</p>
