        <h2 class="ms-title">Sosun Mart<br>Comes to Mal&eacute;</h2>
        <p class="ms-body">We expanded with Sosun Mart &mdash; bringing a new retail format closer to the neighbourhoods of the capital. Shorter distances, more choices, and the same quality Maldivians had come to expect. SOSUN was becoming part of the everyday routine.</p>
