        <p class="ms-chapter">Building Partnerships</p>
        <h2 class="ms-title">Sosun Fihaara<br>Hulhumale' Opens</h2>
        <p class="ms-body">As Hulhumale' grew into a city of its own, SOSUN Fihaara grew with it. Our Hulhumale' location extended our reach to a new generation of residents &mdash; families, young professionals, and a community on the rise. The island was expanding; so were we.</p>
